            On GitHub
        </a>
    </div>
</section>

<figure class="text-center my-5">
    <img src="~/img/landing-hero.png" alt="Stylised illustration: C# code on the left transforming into a printed PDF on the right, ruler and pencil overlay."
         class="img-fluid border rounded shadow-sm"
