    <img src="~/img/landing-primitives.png" alt="Diagram: a page being carved into rows, columns and a titled panel, with labels Row(bounds, 3), Stack(bounds, weights), Panel(bounds, title)."
         class="img-fluid border rounded shadow-sm"
